<title>USA: PAB Bankshares to buy shares on open market.</title>
<headline>PAB Bankshares to buy shares on open market.</headline>
<dateline>VALDOSTA, Ga. 1997-06-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>PAB Bankshares Inc said on Tuesday that it expected to acquire shares for the company's dividend reinvestment plan in the open market.</p>
<p>The announcement marks a departure from a previous policy of issuing dividend reinvestment shares from authorized by unissued shares that were approved by shareholders, the company said in a statement.</p>
<p>The bank holding company expects to acquire about 40,000 of its shares annually, beginning with the July 15 reinvestment date.</p>
